description:
More like Cyberpunk 1997

Main Channel ► https://www.youtube.com/c/dolandark

Well Cyberpunk launched and is unfinished, glitchy, and full of bugs. Especially on console. Here's a meme

Inspired by Cyberpunk 2077 on PS4 by Neverthink:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VhvDy8h3FG8

Sources:
Cyberpunk vehicles trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1LlAgvWD948
I was sent a bunch of unsourced glitch videos so if I happened to use one of your glitch gameplay videos in this meme leave a comment and I will add you to the sources :D
